node.text: i know i already posted once on instagram, but i also wanted to give a huge shout to all of you that supported, none of this would’ve happened or been possible without you. each of the guys on the youtube and tiktok side trained their asses off. my opponent was fierce and versatile, something that i most definitely did not expect. each person put a reputation on the line. my trainers liam and tyler pushed me day to day to be able to even compete in this battle, and i couldn’t have done it without them either.
